  • Type Parameters:
    M - TextureMaterial

    public class TextureMaterialBatchRenderer<M extends TextureMaterial>
extends TextureMaterialBatchRendererBase<M>
    TextureMaterialBatchRenderer allows rendering batches of up to 32 rectangles with TextureMaterial in one draw call. Each rectangle has its own translation, rotation and scale.
    Author:
    Miguel Vicente Linares
